pageProduct.name: Swisse Hemp Seed Oil + Turmeric 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Hemp Seed Oil + Turmeric contains raw, cold-pressed, 100% Australian Hemp Seed oil, a naturally rich plant-based source of Omega 3 and 6. Combined with the goodness of antioxidant-rich turmeric, Swisse Hemp Seed Oil + Turmeric provides a balanced source of Omega 3 and 6 essential fatty acids to support nutritional wellbeing.

Swisse Hemp Seed Oil + Turmeric contains raw, cold-pressed, 100% Australian Hemp Seed oil, a naturally rich plant-based source of Omega 3 and 6. Combined with the goodness of antioxidant-rich turmeric, Swisse Hemp Seed Oil + Turmeric provides a balanced source of Omega 3 and 6 essential fatty acids to support nutritional wellbeing.

Size: 60 Capsules

Warnings

Contains soy & sulfites.

Ingredients

HEMP Seed Oil (49%)
Gelling agents (gelatin, glycerin, purified water)
TURMERIC Powder (9%)
Thickeners (hydrogenated vegetable oil and yellow beeswax)
Stabiliser (soy lecithin)
Anti-caking agent (stearic acid)
Colours (iron oxide yellow)
VITAMIN E (Antioxidant)
Colours (beta-carophyllene)

Directions

Two softgel capsules daily.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
